name: Techno Viking Twins
description:
Techno Viking Twins, is a weird game developed during the Create Jam spring edition 2016..

The common theme were "Growth", which lead the group, iSneezed inc., in many different directions, such as Picking up girls, Politicians, and harems.

The explanation for these weird themes, will never leave the groups inner circle, to F****** bad...

But in the end, a rubber duck was squeezed (who got that reference?), and the idea of Vikings, trying to score chicks in Miami, and grow their clan was decided!

Enjoy the game!!! or dont, what the hell, have a nice day then!
